{"tid":441902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"君豪峰首推93伙 290呎折實入場681萬","createTime":"2017-10-20T06:11:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T11:20:16.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3391d7e37cc079abb70caf4d24d819a4d3c384","tid":441902,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"已有5個月未有在香港推出全新樓盤的恒地(0012),旗下鰂魚涌約18個月樓花君豪峰,剛上載首推93伙的價錢,發展商提供最高5%直減折扣(3%即供折扣和2%特別折扣),整批折實平均呎價約2.4萬元,與同系去年9月開售的北角尚譽首批價錢相若。<br />\n<br />\n君豪峰今批首推93伙,單位實用面積介乎290至451方呎,折實入場費最便宜為15樓一伙290方呎D室,折實售價681萬元(折實呎價23485元)。<br />\n至於最貴一伙為36樓實用451方呎F室,價單717萬，折實售價1162萬元(折實呎價25776元)。<br />\n<br />\n記者：林可為"},{"pid":"02b3394783bcda5abfca4da3778fe7fb6e21569e","tid":441902,"uid":55488,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"081fe3810ad23835d8e52c85a4127d01ec563f4b","tid":441902,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:15:37.000Z","msg":"290呎扣埋個22呎露台仔=一入屋咩都睇晒"},{"pid":"bc15f6b192a55b56fd8456412f805c2a9c6f3121","tid":441902,"uid":22644,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:16:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1000萬左右都仲算合理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩 而家搵錢咁易<br />\n洗碗都4-5萬一個月"},{"pid":"e2f04b41f5703e210e01f599e058e615fffdd65e","tid":441902,"uid":78571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:18:09.000Z","msg":"好撚平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fa09c37753a3e12e2dfdd0016f79db32f3fe65","tid":441902,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:20:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be1824b74fbb77d0ffaadce1f5593165561f6f2e","tid":441902,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:31:10.000Z","msg":"算合理"},{"pid":"39894d9b6ef530be634de88fa3744889310397f5","tid":441902,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:32:53.